  <td>3 other DVs (neglect, voice, loyalty forgiveness; same pattern of results observed)</td>
  <td></td>
  <td></td>
  <td>High commitment priming (writing about interdependence to partner) increases forgiveness on hypothetical betrayals compared to low commitment priming (writing about independence)</td>
  <td></td>
  <td></td>
  <td></td>
  <td></td>
